{"id": "e71bccfe-ba74-47d4-a483-eb8716a764b1", "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "How many commit messages are found in repositories that use the Shell programming language and are licensed under Apache-2.0, where each message exists, is shorter than 1,000 characters, and does not begin with 'merge', 'update', or 'test'?"}, {"role": "assistant", "channel": "analysis", "content": ""}, {"role": "assistant", "channel": "commentary", "recipient": "functions.Bash", "content": [{"content_type": "code", "text": "{\n  \"command\": \"sqlite3 '/Users/shreyashankar/Documents/projects/DataAgentBench/query_GITHUB_REPOS/query_dataset/repo_metadata.db' \\\"SELECT DISTINCT language_description FROM languages LIMIT 20\\\"\",\n  \"description\": \"Sample language descriptions\"\n}", "language": "json"}]}, {"role": "tool", "name": "functions.Bash", "content": "The codebase includes: Ruby (22,438 bytes), Shell (465 bytes).\nThis repository is mainly written in Ruby (1,897 bytes), with additional code in Shell (115 bytes).\nThe codebase includes: Ruby (162,002 bytes), Shell (168 bytes).\nThe majority of the code is in Ruby (25,709 bytes), followed by Shell (115 bytes).\nThe majority of the code is in Ruby (4,198 bytes), followed by Shell (115 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (10,174 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (716 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (17,195 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (115 bytes).\nThe majority of the code is in Ruby (12,891 bytes), followed by Shell (2,343 bytes).\nThe majority of the code is in Ruby (5,324 bytes), followed by Shell (115 bytes).\nThe codebase includes: Ruby (8,171 bytes), Shell (131 bytes).\nThis repository is mainly written in Ruby (11,276 bytes), with additional code in Shell (131 bytes).\nThe majority of the code is in Ruby (184,928 bytes), followed by Shell (146 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (12,007 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (179 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (51,928 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (3,165 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (53,705 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (205 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (49,442 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (131 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (74,892 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (173 bytes).\nThe codebase includes: Ruby (11,538 bytes), Shell (862 bytes).\nThe majority of the code is in Ruby (3,705 bytes), followed by Shell (2,867 bytes).\nWhile most of the project is built in Ruby (4,438 bytes), it also incorporates Shell (131 bytes).", "channel": "commentary"}, {"role": "assistant", "channel": "commentary", "recipient": "functions.Bash", "content": [{"content_type": "code", "text": "{\n  \"command\": \"sqlite3 '/Users/shreyashankar/Documents/projects/DataAgentBench/query_GITHUB_REPOS/query_dataset/repo_metadata.db' \\\"SELECT DISTINCT license FROM licenses LIMIT 20\\\"\",\n  \"description\": \"Sample licenses\"\n}", "language": "json"}]}, {"role": "tool", "name": "functions.Bash", "content": "isc\nmit\ncc0-1.0\nepl-1.0\ngpl-2.0\ngpl-3.0\nmpl-2.0\nagpl-3.0\nlgpl-2.1\nlgpl-3.0\nunlicense\napache-2.0\nartistic-2.0\nbsd-2-clause\nbsd-3-clause", "channel": "commentary"}, {"role": "assistant", "channel": "commentary", "recipient": "functions.Bash", "content": [{"content_type": "code", "text": "{\n  \"command\": \"sqlite3 '/Users/shreyashankar/Documents/projects/DataAgentBench/query_GITHUB_REPOS/query_dataset/repo_metadata.db' \\\"SELECT COUNT(*) FROM languages WHERE language_description LIKE '%Shell%'\\\"\",\n  \"description\": \"Count Shell repos\"\n}", "language": "json"}]}, {"role": "tool", "name": "functions.Bash", "content": "659616", "channel": "commentary"}, {"role": "assistant", "channel": "commentary", "recipient": "functions.Bash", "content": [{"content_type": "code", "text": "{\n  \"command\": \"sqlite3 '/Users/shreyashankar/Documents/projects/DataAgentBench/query_GITHUB_REPOS